@startuml
title ComputeInstance Formal Lifecycle

[*] --> Observed
Observed --> Retryable : PROVISIONING, STARTING, STOPPING
Observed --> Active : RUNNING, STOPPED
Observed --> Failed : FAILED, TERMINATED
Active --> DeletePending : delete requested
Retryable --> DeletePending : delete requested
Failed --> DeletePending : delete requested
DeletePending --> Deleted : finalizer removed after delete

state Retryable
state Active
state Failed
state DeletePending
state Deleted
@enduml
